events.text: …I could’ve slept better last night. I can feel my body weakening by the day. Today’s the day, huh? Feels like it’s been just another ordinary Saturday otherwise.
I know I called off work last night for the next week, but I really didn't need to since I'm just gonna end up resetting back to today anyways. But better safe than sorry.
I should see [Wife] and [Daughter] before I leave.
